layer.message:
You are about to delete layer "{name}".

{count, plural, =0 {The layer is empty.} one {# entity will be deleted.} other {# entities will be deleted.}}

All entities in this layer will be permanently lost.

colorGroup.message:
You are about to delete color group "{name}".

{count, plural, =0 {No layers exist in this group.} one {# layer will be deleted.} other {# layers will be deleted.}}

All layers and entities in this color group will be permanently lost.

entities.message:
You are about to merge {count} entities into "{target}".

Sources for merging: {sources}

The source entities will be deleted and all their properties will be transferred to the target entity.

layers.message:
You are about to merge {count} layers into "{target}".

Sources for merging: {sources}

All entities from the source layers will be moved to the target layer and the source layers will be deleted.

colorGroups.message:
You are about to merge {count} color groups into "{target}".

Sources for merging: {sources}

All layers from the source color groups will be moved to the target color group. The source color groups will disappear but layers and entities will be preserved.
